DIMPLLII
DIMPLLII
esspeecee.05.11.08.
[1] My
Midnight monsoon shower
Come: Stealthily,
Dimpllii, I’ll view
Trickling rain drops
On doused face
The delight point
Your dimple.
[2] My
Bohemian windy storm
Come: Boldly,
Dimpllii, I’ll fall upon
Thro’ your unruly hairs
Shyly peeping
The delight point
Your dimple.
[3] My
Flicker thunder light
Come: Majestically
Dimpllii, I’ll captive
Fleeting silhouette
The delight point
Your dimple.
[4] My
Universal euphony
Vocalize: Melody
Dimpllii, I’ll hear
‘Audiophonic-Smile’
The delight point
Your dimple.
[5] From slumberous dream
Dimpllii: Wake me not
From fluffy warm togetherness
The delight point
Your Dimple.

